PCA wait period ends for American Studios . PCA International Inc said Thursday the waiting period for federal antitrust review of its tender for American Studios Inc has expired . PCA ' s subsidiary , ASI Acquisition Corp , began a tender offer of $ 2 . 50 cash for American Studios shares December 20 . The Hart - Scott - Rodino Act prohibits certain stock buys unless certain information is given to the antitrust division of the Department of Justice and the Federal Trade Commission and unless waiting periods expire . PCA ' s offer for American Studio shares and withdrawal rights are scheduled to expire January 22 . 
